Package: visiaCat
Type: Package
Title: VisIA - Computerized Adaptive Testing
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jose M. Ramirez <ramirezsanchezjosem@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Jose M. Ramirez <ramirezsanchezjosem@gmail.com>
Description: Implements a complete simulation of a Computerized Adaptive Test 
    (CAT) based on Item Response Theory (IRT). This project uses an 
    item bank and a set of anchor items from the VisIA Project to demonstrate 
    a full CAT workflow, from item selection to ability estimation. 
    Developed as a personal portfolio piece to showcase best practices in 
    R package development and psychometric modeling.
